snippet.title: Hazel Kate Quinn
snippet.description:
I am doing some renovating.  Making some new videos to replace older ones, with newer, fresher perspectives for how to survive narcissistic abuse.  Again, I am only one of millions who have dealt with this.  Narcissistic abuse survivors are everywhere, from Hollywood to around the corner from you. 
I am no doctor or therapist, so I don't claim to have all answers. I'm a work in progress, like all of us are, no matter how long we've been on any path of recovery.  All of us want to live happy, healthy lives and while it takes work, it isn't impossible.  Narcissistic(or "Narc" for short) abuse has many layers, and none of it is easy.  It's not something anyone can just "snap out of."  But we can embrace better things as we walk away from what doesn't work for us anymore.  Music is one of the ways that helps me, so often you will see music videos here as well.  Healing  is possible from any kind of abuse, addiction, other trauma or mental illness.  Namaste!!!

snippet.title: Diamond Stylz
snippet.description: Diamond Stylz is one of the premier voices of the millennial black trans community.  She started her activism at 17 when she won a First Amendment rights lawsuit against the Indianapolis Public School system. A victory, with the help of the ACLU, that allows her to go to the prom in a gender-affirming gown instead of a tuxedo. At 19, she was the first openly trans woman to attend the legendary HBCU Jackson State University where she honed her passion for activism. Currently, Diamond is the Executive Director of Black Trans Women Inc, a national non-profit that is led by Black trans women focused on social advocacy, positive visibility, and building strong leadership among Black trans women. Diamond is the host and producer of Marsha's Plate, a weekly podcast that centers on trans-inclusive pro-black feminism and pop culture. I have worked with ABC, BET, SXSW, Stanford Univ, Essence, The Root, Aljazeera, and more.   Any Business Inquiries email me @ diamondstylz@gmail.com

snippet.title: Bailey Rushlow
snippet.description:
hi. i'm Bailey. welcome to my channel full of stories - stories wrapped in lyrics and melodies and thoughts that hopefully make you think, make you feel, and ultimately - help you heal. music is a beautiful language and whether I'm interpreting someone else's work in a cover or singing something I've written, the goal is to take you out of your world for a few minutes and put you in mine. 

long story short, i'm an acoustic pop singer, musician, producer and i create everything you hear online - start to finish - in my room. i consider myself the janitor *and* the CEO of the bailey rushlow music business, because i wear all the hats, and honestly i love being able to create with my life. i'm a Nashville native, currently writing a book, and can't wait to share more of my covers, collaborations, originals and music videos with you this year

i'm happy you're here (:

snippet.title: xNativePirate
snippet.description:
Helloee!

Very nice of you to read my boring description! 
Since you are on this side of my channel I guess you want to know something more about me, heh? :3
Well, I'm a 17 year old girl from a tinie tiny little country in Europe called the Netherlands or Holland or whatever you prefer to call it. And that's about everything you need to know. 
Just kidding!
My name is Amy and I created this channel on the 7th of September, 2012. 
I come here to escape my personal life and share my creativity with the world. 
I might not be as creative as some people out there but I still enjoy making videos whenever I have time on my hands. 
Other than editing I enjoy horseriding and writing stories on Wattpad, you can find me there by my old username : XxElsaxSnowQueenxX

Previously known as: 
-HollyJSinclair Fan
-XxElsaxSnowQueenxX

I like to change my username :) Although I might stick with my current one, I quite like it.

Are you still here? Well, thanks for staying with me!

snippet.description:
Já pensou em um canal cheinho de novidades apenas de fics? 
Aqui você poderá divulgar sua fic e ganhar seu trailer!
Sim, é isto mesmo, um canal criado apenas para você ficar atento no mundos dos fãs de plantão que dedicam aquelas horinhas do dia para escrever sobre os mais variados assuntos.
Serão feitos cerca de dois Trailers e um OTP Vídeo por mês, todos serão postados e divulgados no canal. Mais para frente irei adicionar outros conteúdos, como resenhas de fanfictions, críticas, regras de português, entrevistas com autores veteranos de fanfics, além de outras ajudinhas para fazer da sua fic um sucesso!

snippet.title: Chris Fernandez
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Chris. I'm a final year film student at the Westminster Film School, University of Westminster, based in Coventry. For those who don't know, I hold the ambition to write and direct movie musicals as well as compose the original music for them.

Here you can find videos from everything I'm into: 
- Film trailers and clips from freelance projects and personal projects.
- Cover videos of songs from musical theatre and pop culture as well as film scores (MIDI remakes and original soundtracks)
- Motion graphics from freelance projects as well as logo remakes.
- COMING SOON: DIY videos of projects I build in my garden/workshop!

While I've diverted all efforts to my education and filmmaking, all of which is my journey to (hopefully) becoming a professional film director, I still upload occationally so please subscribe to keep up with what I'm doing!

snippet.title: Maz Jobrani
snippet.description:
MAZ JOBRANI is a founding member of The Axis of Evil Comedy Tour which first aired on Comedy Central. He has had three Showtime specials, Brown and Friendly, I Come In Peace, and most recently, I'M NOT A TERRORIST BUT I'VE PLAYED ONE ON TV. 

In February of 2015 he had a book come out with the same title, I'M NOT A TERRORIST BUT I'VE PLAYED ONE ON TV, published by Simon & Schuster. He performs stand-up live around the world, including the Middle East where he performed in front of the King of Jordan, as well as the White House where he had the privilege of introducing First Lady Michelle Obama.

Maz has also performed stand up on THE TONIGHT SHOW and THE LATE LATE SHOW WITH CRAIG FERGUSON. Most recently, Maz starred as the title character in the award-winning indie comedy, JIMMY VESTVOOD: AMERIKAN HERO, a film which he co-wrote and produced.  Maz has been featured on CNN, the BBC, The New York Times, and Time Magazine. He is also a regular panelist on NPR’s WAIT WAIT DON'T TELL ME.

Welcome to the epictasticness that is this channel! My name is Joshua Drake, ADHD & autistic and I have had a passion for movies ever since I was a young child and my goal on this channel is to talk movies (old & new), TV shows and music.

Whether it's talking some of my favorite films like Harry Potter, Ray, The Dark Knight, BvS, talking some of my favorite shows like The Simpsons, Family Guy or my favorite ever SpongeBob SquarePants or talking about some music, I hope to entertain you guys by giving you guys my honest opinions on these things good, bad or mixed, I hope you enjoy what you come here for on this channel and you guys all stay awesome, keep it cool and Join the Epictasticness. 

Want to send fan mail?

Joshua Drake 
1922 Batts Lane - Apt B
Clarksville TN, 37042

My Rating System ranges from JD Rainbow Seal of Approval to JD Get Out My Face Club

snippet.title: krishnan srinivasan
snippet.description:
A Fine art Photographer and a Distance Skater.
It took quite a hard way to learn about life & start something of my own ..
I was also learning about the hurdles one would have when sticking to his passion..
after all that & as an ongoing process....
Here I'm creating videos on skating & Fine art photography , as vlogs on public interest.
I seriously didn't worry about number of views & subscribers .. like I did at the beginning..
Hope you guys find it helpful :)

snippet.title: eMZet Martez
snippet.description:
Hallo, Hello e Buongiorno, 
ich bin eMZet Martez: Wortklangmaschine, Reimathlet aus Mainz Gonsenheim.

Ich bin ein kleiner Rapper, der versucht, auf diesem Weg etwas größer zu werden. 
Ich mache alles selbst, dh. ich schreibe Lyricz, komponiere, Sample und mastere 
auch meine Musik. Aber bisher nur als Hobby. 
Der Hauptfokus liegt natürlich klar in meiner Familie, der ich hier alles widme.
Besonderer Dank an alle Abonnenten und welche, die es werden möchten.
Viel Spaß beim reinhören

Nay, a short life but a merry one shall be my motto"

snippet.title: Michael Butchin
snippet.description:
I have recently been encouraged by a friend to use my channel to speak out for Atheism, Skepticism, and Rational Thought.  And so I shall.

But for those few of you that have tuned in to watch my progress in Martial Arts practice, fear not; I fully intend to continue tracking my training progress. And perhaps I may throw in a few of my own thoughts about the Martial Arts (despite my limited qualifications to do so) as well.

But speaking out against superstition and Religious Faith and, the harm they do is a necessary and important task. As was recently made clear to me, I have been sitting on the sidelines for far too long.

I'm rather new at this, so I hope the quality of my videos will improve over time as I learn to edit and so forth.

Ego Immitior Quia Toleraro.

snippet.title: the14thmoonofuranus
snippet.description:
Hi I'm Miranda :-) and I am bedridden with Severe ME/CFS which I have had since 2001. My channel is mainly about this condition & also about what keeps me motivated. It now includes Flosstube videos for cross stitchers! 😀 I hope my videos are of use to someone, I appreciate every viewing and read every comment. I'll reply if I can 🙂

I am deeply appreciative of all the great talent here on YouTube and the people who work so hard to put these videos together. My playlist collection has got me through some very low, lonely and boring moments whilst being stuck in bed every moment of my day. Well done to all uploaders :-) xxxxx 

For those who question the seriousness of the illness ME please watch the Voices From the Shadows film.

All the best & good health to you all xxx :-)

Join me on Instagram https://instagram.com/mirrie_creates?igshid=1m7aodi3hgq7e

#ME #CFS #MEawareness #pwme #millionsmissing
